headline: IFF to Release Second Quarter 2025 Results on Aug. 5, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, July 09, 2025--IFF (NYSE:IFF) today announced that it will release its second quarter 2025 earnings results following the market close on Tuesday, Aug. 5, 2025. The management team will host a live webcast on Wednesday, Aug. 6, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. ET to discuss results and outlook with the investor community.
